                    <history>
                        <origin/>
                        <provenance>
                            <p>Previous French owner may have been Jean Varsy, a merchant settled at
                                Rosetta before the French expedition of 1798-99, a pupil of de Sacy,
                                in business at Alexandria and Marseilles, and a contributor to the
                                Journal Asiatique up to 1850.</p>
                        </provenance>
                        <provenance>
                            <p/>
                        </provenance>
